parameters.name: PDSTIME
parameters.description:
This field contains time in PDS format:                    
                        yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm:ss.sssZ.

parameters.name: R
parameters.description:
Saturn to spacecraft range (positive away from Saturn) 
                        in the unit of Saturn's radius.

parameters.name: LON
parameters.description: Kronocentric east longitude, completing the left handed, orthogonal set, in degree.

parameters.name: LOCTIME
parameters.description: Spacecraft local time in decimal hours.
